Package edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.model.entity

Class Post

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.model.entity.Post
  • @Entity
public class Post
extends java.lang.Object
    Post entity in the database to store information regarding the posts users can make to the community wall. The posts will have information in regards to the creation date for the content/ pictures a user may post.
